{"tid":2152013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英獲准保釋離開旺角警署","createTime":"2020-08-11T16:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T23:25:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7d985e43656e960aa74560c27ad9f120413f2f","tid":2152013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543199-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543199-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=24ee539e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543199-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8340569f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543199-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n被扣查約40小時的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英獲准保釋，凌晨約12時離開旺角警署，他被大批本地及國際傳媒包圍採訪，他表示「無嘢講」，及後登上私家車離開。<br />\n<br />\n十數名市民在旺角警署外，手持《蘋果日報》頭版，高叫口號「撐蘋果，撐到底」聲援黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n其他被捕人士昨晚亦陸續獲准保釋，包括前香港眾志成員周庭。《蘋果日報》報道，黎智英次子黎耀恩、壹傳媒行政總裁張張劍虹等高層，昨晚亦獲釋。"},{"pid":"cddfa2f6c319c236d4024e088ee12b5964822f80","tid":2152013,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d7d985e43656e960aa74560c27ad9f120413f2f","tid":2152013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543199-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543199-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=24ee539e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543199-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8340569f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543199-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />